<i>♪ We're not gonna take it</i>

920
00:55:17.037 --> 00:55:19.695
<i>♪ No. we ain't gonna take it</i>

921
00:55:20.524 --> 00:55:25.563
<i>♪ We're not gonna
take it anymore ♪</i>

922
